{"parentUuid":"ccce3d44-1b08-4bd8-b258-12875ac1e55b","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01HC2K6GAVGkuGwhhpiDzZ7Y","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"`CheckTaskValid` 检查 Job 中各 TaskRole 的实际可用副本数是否满足最小可用要求。\n\n**逻辑流程：**\n\n1. **快速跳过检查**（[job_info.go:999](pkg/scheduler/api/job_info.go#L999)）：如果 `MinAvailable < TaskMinAvailableTotal`，说明 Job 层面的最小可用数比所有 Task 的最小可用数之和还小，存在矛盾配置，直接返回 `true` 跳过校验。\n\n2. **统计各 TaskRole 的实际可用数**（[job_info.go:1003-1012](pkg/scheduler/api/job_info.go#L1003-L1012)）：遍历 `TaskStatusIndex`，将处于以下状态的 Task 计入统计：\n   - `AllocatedStatus`（已分配资源的状态，如 Bound/Running 等）\n   - `Succeeded`（已成功）\n   - `Pipelined`（流水线中）\n   - `Pending`（等待中）\n\n3. **校验每个 TaskRole 是否达到 minAvailable**（[job_info.go:1017-1023](pkg/scheduler/api/job_info.go#L1017-L1023)）：遍历 `ji.TaskMinAvailable` 配置，对每个 TaskRole：\n   - 跳过 `minAvailable == 0` 的 TaskRole\n   - 若该 TaskRole 没有任何可用 Task，或实际数量 `< minAvailable`，返回 `false`\n\n4. 所有 TaskRole 都满足条件则返回 `true`。\n\n**核心语义**：确保 Job 中每种角色（如 `worker`、`ps`）都有足够数量的副本处于\"有效\"状态，这是 Gang Scheduling 细粒度检查的一部分——不仅看整体 `minAvailable`，还看每个 TaskRole 各自是否达标。"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":3,"cache_creation_input_tokens":6124,"cache_read_input_tokens":11289,"output_tokens":592,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":6124,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"requestId":"req_011CZovjnnP6i4LeFEVTGmZS","type":"assistant","uuid":"362530bc-4e9a-4201-a35a-230d66d00b0a","timestamp":"2026-04-07T06:20:52.523Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"claude-vscode","cwd":"/Users/xuwentao/Projects/github/volcano","sessionId":"814710e0-c005-483c-bcb2-727b2e09f73c","version":"2.1.92","gitBranch":"feat-capacity-dra"}
